Fred Esmelton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fred_Esmelton 0 Fred Esmelton (22 June 1872 – 23 October 1933) was an Australian-born American film actor. He appeared in 30 films between years 1916 and 1931. He was born in Melbourne, Victoria and died in Los Angeles, California.
